=== Other Stuff

Reduplication of the last syllabe is using as intensifier ("very")

== Conditionals

If/then phrases are made with an interrogative phrase and then an "if":

“if i wanted, i would've done it” = (INT.PAST PERF done it if PAST want it)

== Negatives

Negating is adding *gyi* before a word.

Negating a verb is adding *gyi* and eliding the first consonant: _fepsi_ becomes _*gyi*\epsi_

