= Śácamþaśá

Originally the language of the Triarchy of Śácamþa, a government in the Jałar planet, *Śácamþaśá* (also known as *ŚCŚ*) has been a co-official language in *Þunan Qumreá* and is the sole official language of the underwater ŋation *Maraśa*.

== Script

ŚCŚ uses a syllabary called *Þeurilá*. It is written right-to-left.

== Phonology

ŚCŚ is romanized phonetically. This guide uses the romanization.

